text: Rachel Miriam Marcia Free Rinast (born 2 June 1991) is a Swiss footballer who plays as a defender for 1. FC Köln. She rejoined Köln after spending the 2012–13 season with SC 07 Bad Neuenahr. ==Career== Since her debut at the 2015 Algarve Cup, she has been a member of the Switzerland women's national football team.Portrait in the Swiss Football Association's page She was playing in the German second division for Köln, when Swiss selectors discovered her mother was from St. Gallen and called her up.
